<plot>Margaret is 14 weeks pregnant. As we follow her through the day of her abortion at a London clinic, we hear from four other women who have also made the choice to have a termination. As we hear their stories, we are left in no doubt that there is nothing black and white about abortion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?021402</url></doc>
